it.sauronsoftware.ftp4j

Interface FTPTextualExtensionRecognizer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultTextualExtensionRecognizer, ParametricTextualExtensionRecognizer

    public interface FTPTextualExtensionRecognizer
    This interface describes how to implement a textual extension recognizer, which can be plugged into a FTPClient object calling its setTextualExtensionsRecognizer() method.
    Author:
    Carlo Pelliccia
    See Also:
    FTPClient.setTextualExtensionRecognizer(FTPTextualExtensionRecognizer)

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean isTextualExt(String ext)
      This method returns true if the given file extension is recognized to be a textual one.
